      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"2. BENTLEY REX turned in a modest effort most recently when eighth at Q Lakeside over 457m behind Kachina Ripple (26.55) in a Restricted WIN. Was in the money prior to that. Has a win and four minor placings from five starts from this draw. Has claims if he runs up to expectations. 1. MARSUPILAMI had a tricky draw last time and although midfield in fourth wasn't far away finishing 1.3 lengths from the winner (16.89). Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. Bold showing expected. 5. DAWN SURE CAN finished fifth last time at Q Lakeside but could not have been more impressive a few runs back in her superb 25.28 win at Q Lakeside over 457m. Top win three back and rates a key player again. 4. LEE FITZ placed last time (28.13) at Casino in a Grade 5, finishing second and beaten 2.75 lengths. Already a winner from this draw.\",\"runners\":[2,1,5,4],\"exclusive\":false}",
